[info] Activation of plug-in SEC Inline Transforms successful, version 19.2. - transforms/SEC

[DQC.US.0167.10099] In the statement 001 - Statement - Condensed Balance Sheets the filer has defined multiple roots calculation elements that do not have a valid calculation tree defined. The root element LiabilitiesAndStockholdersEquity has sibling root elements of us-gaap:LiabilitiesCurrent, us-gaap:Assets in the filing. The sibling element us-gaap:LiabilitiesCurrent should appear as a calculation descendant of LiabilitiesAndStockholdersEquity. This sibling element(s) are defined as calculation descendants in the US GAAP taxonomy.
